PARAMEDIC: Advanced field trauma care

Category: Medical
Base skill: 40% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

A step above First Aid: stabilizing critically wounded patients in
the field, recognizing and treating shock and internal bleeding, and
keeping someone alive long enough to reach a hospital or a Medical
Doctor. Common among Coalition medics, mercenary company corpsmen,
and anyone whose job puts them near a battlefield.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

